{"tid":1828794,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"麻煩各位幫我將呢個畫面推比所有黃區議員","createTime":"2020-01-18T07:21:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-18T16:47:04.000Z","uid":270506,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"6f6105be6f55c5e35ddfa4fcea51d6f28e526d65","tid":1828794,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:21:58.000Z","msg":"各位黃區議員唔該由呢一刻開始比心機做嘢同街坊建立關係，少數派而家係<strong>出盡全力籠絡人心</strong>，以下係今日鄭泳舜寫揮春再加幫人做選民登記嘅深水埗街站<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7VgK2Sa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7VgK2Sa.png&h=dd6c2ea1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔單止深水埗，紅磡都有落選少數派喺度擺街站寫揮春，照我觀察目前對家嘅曝光係多過我哋好多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔該各位區議員尤其係素人要開始有危機感，對家嘅目的係今年立法會選舉翻盤，同埋喺下次區選攞返你哋嘅議席！你哋做嘢要勤力過對家，先至可以穩固同擴張反共陣營嘅勢力，千祈唔好鬆懈，逢親節日一定要鬥早喺人流多嘅地方擺街站派下嘢，量血壓呢啲都要定期做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cc16968aa1af30bc55189dd82ed4fbafdb0f07d","tid":1828794,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:25:13.000Z","msg":"P牌仔推唔到，麻煩各位幫手推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60ca2533abfe1bc584d0427531e9e5e9e2e392c6","tid":1828794,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:26:47.000Z","msg":"【突發】民集交代明天&quot;天下制裁集會&quot;安排<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1828790\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1828790</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea8b534314a756a8d24bcd6ff5fb731c6b444471","tid":1828794,"uid":270506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:29:50.000Z","msg":"各位巴絲打唔好Like完就算，幫手推推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce0860354d5a9c420ea7309d94f013b867df9310","tid":1828794,"uid":61082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-18T07:41:04.000Z","msg":"推推推推推推推推推"},{"pid":"64c7d3f4846b8977a572e4985270e57d20ad3e3a","tid":1828794,"uid":1477